<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢- لا تكن رطبا فتعصر، ولا يابسا فتكسر.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣- <span class="c3">{لَا تَعْتَذِرُوا الْيَوْمَ}</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
