<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">ماذا يراد بصيغ النهي الآتية:</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>١- <span class="c3">{وَلَا تَمْشِ فِي الْأَرْضِ مَرَحًا}</span> .<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٢- <span class="c3">{وَلَا يُضَارَّ كَاتِبٌ وَلَا شَهِيدٌ}</span> .<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٣- <span class="c3">{وَلا تَجْعَلْ يَدَكَ مَغْلُولَةً إِلَى عُنُقِكَ}</span> .<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
